a. Through the Inspection Officers to discontinue the practice of leaving the “Date Received” blank in the Acceptance and Inspection Reports and Delivery Receipts. Indicate the exact date the items, materials or project was/were delivered, accepted and inspected;

b. For the accounting unit to carefully examine that supporting documents for payments are complete and proper and impose liquidated damages for delayed deliveries and;

